https://github.com/aspnet/AspNetCore/blob/2e4274cb67c049055e321c18cc9e64562da52dcf/src/Components/Shared/test/TestRenderer.cs

I have extended the TestRender as follow:

```
        public async Task<TComponent> CreateRenderedComponentAsync<TComponent>(bool requiresAuthorization) where TComponent : IComponent
        {
            var component = this.InstantiateComponent<TComponent>();

            if (requiresAuthorization)
            {
                var authComponent = WrapInAuthorizeView(context => builder => builder.AddContent(0, component));
                var authComponentId = this.AssignRootComponentId(authComponent);

                await this.RenderRootComponentAsync(authComponentId);
            }
            else
            {
                var componentId = this.AssignRootComponentId(component);

                await this.RenderRootComponentAsync(componentId);
            }

            return component;
